Text:
One day, Natsume is holding a book signing for
a new release...

Thank you for all of your support! Okay, next
please!
...Heh.
My, aren't you cute! May I ask your name?

I am Nenechi... Member of the 5th Unit, she who is
bathed in the glow of twilight...
Um... S-So your name is...?

I-I shall say it once more... I am Nenechi, she who
is bathed in the glow of—

Gah!!! This is way too hard! I tried to say it cool
like Shadow does, but I just can't get it right.
Wha?! Sh-Shadow?!
...Ahem. So your name is Nenechi?

Yep, Nenechi! Or Momosuzu Nene, to be precise!
Good afternene!
G-Good afternene...?

(For some reason I feel like I'm trying to match
her energy here... Who the heck is this girl?)

(It seems that she knows of Master Shadow, but she
must not be a member of the Garden if she isn't using
his proper title...)

(The most likely possibility is...she's a friend of
Master Shadow. One that the rest of us had no
idea existed—)
...Uh, hello? You okay?
Oh! S-Sorry about that!

Okay, then sign your autograph right here!
"To the amazing and ultra cute Nenechi"!
Alright. To the amazing and ultra cute Nenechi...
Yay! Thanks!

(In any case, so long as she's an acquaintance of
Master Shadow, I must learn more about her as well...)

Say, Nenechi...would you have a moment to speak with
me after my book signing?
What?! Are you asking me on a—

Don't get the wrong idea. There are just a few things
I'd like to ask you, that's all.

Aww... But sure! I'll tell you whatever you want to
hear!
...Aha, there she is! Over here!

I'm so sorry! That took a little longer than
expected. Did I keep you waiting?

Not at all! So, what'd you want to ask? Just ask
away, I'll answer anything as long as it isn't too
prying!

Alright then, Nenechi... How much do you know about
Mas—I mean, Shadow?

Um, let's see... Well, he goes to the Midgar Academy
for Dark Knights, right? Shadow...or well, Cid.
...A-Anything else?

He gets treated like a dog a lot, and he's up to his
ears in pretty girls, like those Seven Shadows.
I-I see...

(She knows of Princess Alexia and the Seven Shadows?!
Who is this girl?)

(An agent of the Cult? A mole sent to investigate
Master Shadow? Or maybe even—)

They really are amazing up close. Like huge,
magnificent, ginormous! Hey, can you do a
little jump for me?

(She sounds so young! Someone this guileless could
never be part of the Cult...)

L-Let's change the subject. Maybe you can tell me
a little more about you?

Me? Well, I do live streams and stuff so that I can
be an idol loved by oodles of people!

Like an energy drink for the masses! C'mon, Natsume!
Fwshhh!
O-Oh, okay... Fwshhh...

("Idol"? "Live stream"? Can't say I'm familiar
with a lot of these words she's using.)

(I've heard "Energy drink" before, as a bit of
my lord's Shadow Wisdom... Oh!)

(Could these "idols" and "live streams" also be
wisdom Master Shadow passed on to her?!)

Pl-Please give me some more details! Tell me more
about yourself, about "idols" and the rest!
Hmm...details? I'm not so good at explaining stuff.

...Aha! The fastest way would probably be just to
show you!
Huh? Show me what?

Which means, it's time for a special surprise
concert! I hope you're all excited!

Nene moves to a conspicuous spot in the cafe and
begins to sing and dance without backing music.

Sh-She's singing and dancing? This is just way too
random...
But...she does have a nice voice.
What the...? Were they having an event today?

Hey, she ain't half bad! Keep it up, kid! Sing your
heart out!

Thanks, everyone! I'd say this is the perfect time
for another song!
Yeah!!!

When did all these people get here?! And they're
all really into it!
...Hehe, but I can see why.

(A singing voice and dance moves like that aren't
things you master overnight. They prove she's put
in a lot of work.)

(Her dedication and sincerity are plain to see,
so the people here can't help but want to cheer
her on. Is this what she meant about being an
idol?)

Nene's impromptu concert ends, and the satisfied
crowd disperses.

Phew... That was fun! So what did you think of my
show?

It was very good. I think I understand you quite
well now.
Ohhh... Is that what this was all about?

Yes. I'm sure it was this innocence of yours that
made Master Shadow decide to befriend you, hehe.

You do know I'm not actually friends with him, right?
I've never even met him in person.
...What?

I just saw him in a stream with my fans. He was super
awesome!

There's that "stream" word again! What exactly
does that mean—
Ack!
What now?!

It's almost time for me to stream! Oh no, I gotta go,
like right now!
Alright, I'll see you later! Bye-bye!
H-Hold on, Nenechi! Wait!

...She's gone. And there's still so much I don't know
about her, or these "streams"...

Her mind filled with unanswered questions, yet also
feeling somehow invigorated after the performance,
Natsume heads home—
